        </ul>
    </div>`,
    medium: `<div class="summary-content">
        <h1>AI Technology Trends 2024</h1>
        <h2>Key Points</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Generative AI sees major improvements in accuracy and efficiency</li>
            <li>Edge AI enables faster, more private computing</li>
            <li>Global AI regulations being developed</li>
